{"tid":1031192,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"係Windows 10找回Windows 相片檢視器","createTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:00.000Z","uid":175335,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe2a8915da06a97f0bc607823d8021fc9e99b43","tid":1031192,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"update 到 windows 10 之後發現唔見咗Windows 相片檢視器，只有嗰個垃圾圖片app。滑鼠右click 都唔見Windows 相片檢視器。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wn8egzu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwn8egzu.jpg&h=afa9c885&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今次教程就係教大家點樣將Windows 相片檢視器重新開啟。<br />\n第一步：win+R 打開執行輸入 regedit<br />\n第二步：找出 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows Photo Viewer\\Capabilities\\FileAssociations。跟住路徑一個step一個step就可以搵到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27b3Uoj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27b3Uoj.jpg&h=8d21bf36&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第三步：右click -新增-字串值(S)-改名(.bmp)-再點擊.bmp右click修改(M)-數值資料(V)輸入PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff-確定<br />\n其他格式輸入如下：<br />\n.bmp - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.dib - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.gif - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.jfif - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.jpe - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.jpeg -PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.jpg - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.png - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n.wdp - PhotoViewer.FileAssoc.Tiff<br />\n入曬之後就係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wm6vzzn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwm6vzzn.jpg&h=3fc7f2ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後你右click你幅相，就會發現 windows 相片檢視器出翻嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UBO5HL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UBO5HL.jpg&h=e6878f89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56229772631866eb437dbab0d72e95311c4d62b5","tid":1031192,"uid":175335,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解要俾負評我"},{"pid":"af2ca2b50907c7fa98c634cdcfec871921601ce2","tid":1031192,"uid":86508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"download 呢個.reg double click 已經搞掂<br />\n<a href=\"https://walker-a.com/archives/3131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwalker-a.com%2Farchives%2F3131&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHDyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=24d442cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://walker-a.com/archives/3131</a>"}]}